// C3: Physical sensing components
instance InternalTemperatureSensor1 : DTDFVocab:SensingComponent [
    base:desc "First internal temperature sensor monitoring the insulated styrofoam box's internal environment with analog readings in °C, interfaced via Raspberry Pi GPIO or ADC module."
